						               													<description>This picture book and game tells the story of Uproar in Heaven. Sun Wukong returned after learning and found golden cudgel while he explores the Dragon Palace, signed the book of life and death at King Yama's place, and uproar in the Heaven.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Different adventure levels combined mathematical knowledge into the game to help children enlighten thinking, master knowledge, develop good habits of independent learning and active thinking. 6 games correspond to 6 education points: Master arithmetic within 20; Understand Spatial Transformation; Recognize shapes and locations change; Recognize plane figures and understand regularity. It also includes a reaction ability training activity.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To win 6 levels in the game:&amp;#10;- Treasure Hunt in Dragon Palace: Help Wukong escape the Dragon Palace.&amp;#10;- The book of Life and Death: Fold the book of life and death&amp;#10;- Uproar in Heaven: Defeat the rivals&amp;#10;- Casting spells in Peach Garden: Freeze the seven fairies&amp;#10;- Erlang Shen: Get to know the secret of 72 transfigurations&amp;#10;- Escape the Cauldron: Help Wukong get out of the Cauldron&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After you complete each level, insert the manual card to the corresponding page in the passport comes with the game. The first one who collects all 6 manual cards and fills the passport is the winner of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
